<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/janet-daby> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Janet Daby was the Parliamentary Under-Secretary of State (Minister for Children and Families) at the Department for Education between 9 July 2024 and 7 September 2025. She was elected as the Labour MP for Lewisham East in June 2018."@en .
